data.meta_description: 46 likes, 0 comments - milimila_ on January 20, 2024: "#sentimentalsaturday The celebration of Heroes' Day coincides with the opening ceremonies for Cabral’s Centennial Celebrations, with President Jose Maria Neves, former President and Commander and revoluntionary leader, Pedro Pires on hand to kick off the year long celebration! Amilcar Cabral's 100th birthday is on Septeber 12th, 2024. Vivi Cabo Verde! Viva Cabral!".
